The Keiser Report  No. 205
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Thursday, 03 November 2011


[sebaygo1]


This time Max and Stacy discuss the new world order in which we're all Greeks because we didn't see the signs in 1969 - "Make Love, Not Debt." 

In the second half of the show, Max Keiser interviews Birgitta Jonsdottir, about the true state of transparency, banking and economy in the latest IMF poster child, Iceland.
